Phobia sensed an opportunity coming he didn't know what a Vok was, it 
sounded more like a chicken sound then a race.

"Think about this, if Rowdy was changed by these Vok as you called 
them, and Megatron is bringing him back to the Decepticons then 
logically Megatron could be working with the Vok." he reached down 
and took the component before KitKat had the chance to take a closer 
look at it. "And if Megatron is working with the Vok then that could 
explain his incompetence." Phobia gave KitKat a sly knowing 
glance "He hasn't won because he has bigger plans worked out with the 
Vok."

--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, logomorph@h... wrote:
> ::KitKat::
> She looked at the component, then up to Phobia. "He was one of us. 
> He's an old friend of Quickstrikes.  He helped us rescue 
Quickstrike 
> from the Vok cave.  But Rowdy was caught by the vok and changed 
into 
> one of them.  He's now talking to Megatron."  she drained the 
energon 
> and stood up on all fours. "Any ideas on this?"
>

> > Phobia reached into one of his crates, pulled out an electronic

> > in front of KitKat.
